<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Shan Online Store</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #eef4ff;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --primary: #0d6efd;
        --primary-dark: #0b5ed7;
        --text: #212529;
        --muted: #6c757d;
      }
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      html,
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eef4ff 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
        color: var(--text);
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      .container {
        width: min(1100px, 96%);
        margin: 28px auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }
      .logo {
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: var(--primary);
      }
      .logo img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        display: block;
      }
      nav {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
      }
      nav a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .hero {
        background: var(--surface);
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 36px 28px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(26, 54, 126, 0.08);
        text-align: center;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }
      .lead {
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .hero-actions {
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 26px;
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background: var(--primary-dark);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }
      .secondary {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 26px;
        color: var(--primary);
        border: 1px solid var(--primary);
        border-radius: 999px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .card {
        background: var(--surface);
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.05);
      }
      .card h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .card p {
        margin: 10px 0 0;
      }
      .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 10px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .footer-links a {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer-links a:hover {
        color: var(--primary);
      }
      footer {
        margin-top: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 760px) {
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        header {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <a class="brand" href="Index.html">
          <div class="logo">
            <img src="images/shAn.png" alt="Shan Online Store logo" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-weight: 700;">Shan Online Store</div>
            <div style="font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted);">Fast local shopping</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <nav>
          <a href="Index.html">Home</a>
          <a href="HTML.html">Store</a>
          <a href="delivery.html">Delivery</a>
          <a href="order-history.html">Order History</a>
          <a href="Pay.html">Pay</a>
        </nav>
      </header>
      <main>
        <section class="hero">
          <p class="eyebrow">Local storefront</p>
          <h1>Shop with confidence and checkout in one simple demo website.</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Explore featured products, schedule fast delivery, and view your recent orders with a polished storefront experience.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn" href="HTML.html">Browse Store</a>
            <a class="secondary" href="delivery.html">Delivery Info</a>
          </div>
        </section>
        <div class="grid">
          <section class="card">
            <h2>Featured store</h2>
            <p class="muted">Browse sample items and choose the ones you want to buy.</p>
            <p>Visit the store page to view product cards, prices, and a direct checkout link.</p>
          </section>
          <section class="card">
            <h2>Delivery details</h2>
            <p class="muted">Choose a shipping option and keep delivery times clear.</p>
            <p>The delivery page highlights same-day, express, and standard shipping choices with local pricing.</p>
          </section>
          <section class="card">
            <h2>Order history</h2>
            <p class="muted">Track recent activity and order status at a glance.</p>
            <p>View formatted order records and delivery updates to stay organized.</p>
          </section>
          <section class="card">
            <h2>Easy checkout</h2>
            <p class="muted">Complete payment details with a simple, mobile-friendly form.</p>
            <p>Use the checkout page to simulate a payment and confirm your order.</p>        </section>
          <section class="card">
          <h2>Contact Information</h2>
          <p style="margin: 8px 1; color: var(--muted);">Phone: +1 (876) 850-2944</p>
          <p style="margin: 8px 1; color: var(--muted);">Email: shaninkprint@gmail.com</p>
          <p style="margin: 8px 1; color: var(--muted);">Address: 11 John Street, Kingston, Jamaica</p>
          </section>
        </div>
    </main>
      <footer class="footer">
        <div>
          <a href="Index.html">Home</a> ·
          <a href="HTML.html">Store</a> ·
          <a href="order-history.html">Order History</a> ·
          <a href="Pay.html">Pay</a>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:6px;">Published 2026. Owner: Shanique.</div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
